Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.38,0:00:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.82,0:00:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後成了件大工作呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.72,0:00:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不感到懷念嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.50,0:00:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到會把這個拿出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.40,0:00:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會不知道這是多麼危險的東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.82,0:00:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.35,0:00:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在看護著它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.77,0:00:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此才會成那些孩子今後旅途上需要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.12,0:00:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因果循環啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.83,0:00:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.91,0:00:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘管人類看起來像是重複同樣的錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.04,0:00:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因果絶不是循環的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.20,0:00:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是螺旋般的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.42,0:00:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些孩子不一定會選如你我一樣的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.64,0:01:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.16,0:01:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的靈力竟如此脆弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.48,0:01:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結界輕而易舉就被擊破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.99,0:01:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要為我而戰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.82,0:01:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但無論哪條路我已經
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.20,0:01:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此才要心平氣和地戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.08,0:01:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.42,0:01:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會忘記你的真心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.52,0:01:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的老友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.78,0:01:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少最後能再一次看到你那羞澀的笑容
Comment: Marked=0,0:03:22.32,0:03:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,/-------START--------/
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.32,0:03:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.83,0:03:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.12,0:03:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才一瞬間好像感受到了師傅的念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.75,0:03:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渴望快點得到科羅拉的誇獎而按捺不住了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.96,0:03:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女見習卻能退治惡鬼定會成為這裡的新傳說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.76,0:03:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.51,0:03:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做到的只是堵住獸鬼的巢穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然召喚出了巨大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.98,0:03:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻不能好好使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,徒然讓損害擴大而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.61,0:03:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還不成熟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.95,0:04:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好感動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你的眼睛有點可怕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.49,0:04:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到了什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.79,0:04:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實說我還不知道他們是不是我的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.04,0:04:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.97,0:04:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.42,0:04:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個寺院傷囗沒有合嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.68,0:04:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.52,0:04:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然傷囗已經合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.69,0:04:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 傷囗非常深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉體的傷囗確實合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.28,0:04:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但幽體的傷囗還留在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.40,0:04:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放任不管就會不斷袁弱下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.33,0:04:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚會讓肉體的訇囗再次裂開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.72,0:04:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 能救他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.82,0:04:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘快抬到洋館 讓他服下師傅的靈藥的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家來幫我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無大礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.68,0:05:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是一時沒站穩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.86,0:05:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀倒是可以借你一用 雖然我不情願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.69,0:05:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.14,0:05:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽體之傷即精神之傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.88,0:05:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該會有法忍受的劇痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般的人都無法保持意識清醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.10,0:05:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.26,0:05:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們逃出以後在那裡到底遇到了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.66,0:05:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個傷應該不是獸鬼弄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.00,0:05:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我施上去的護符也不知什麼時候被抹消了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.51,0:05:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是用它揍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.42,0:05:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這東西揍了自認為是天使的怪物一頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.89,0:05:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種 這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.04,0:06:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,區區人類竟有和那種高位靈體戰鬥的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.96,0:06:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷斬殺幽體而獲得此種力量的劍的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.66,0:06:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要因被預言的奇躦而蒙蔽雙眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.16,0:06:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請看看眼前的奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.24,0:06:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他還活著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 這種靈氣的流動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.55,0:06:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林的深處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.36,0:06:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是洋館的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林的結界消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.52,0:06:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喀絲卡小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法露和喀絲卡在這裡等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.36,0:06:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.72,0:06:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是剩下的獸鬼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.98,0:06:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有棘手的東西在洋館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼根本不能比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆有危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.70,0:06:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那些傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.84,0:07:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師 師博大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.85,0:07:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們快攔住她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會錯 那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.78,0:07:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.41,0:07:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋從哪冒出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.38,0:07:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 有人類闖入這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.38,0:07:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女的同伴嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.90,0:07:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.14,0:08:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要揮動那把大劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.68,0:08:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻搖搖晃晃地 真不像話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.82,0:08:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你 為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.54,0:08:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和這個洋館的主人交情很深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.75,0:08:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.96,0:08:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 所以那時會在獸鬼的巢穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.59,0:08:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些使徒不配知我名諱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.09,0:08:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只會說給向5名天使復仇之人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼胡言亂語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.60,0:08:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等這樣啊我想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.85,0:08:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等之主轉生之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.82,0:08:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於該地現身的騎士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.99,0:08:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.07,0:08:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.28,0:09:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們主人的祭品 那個倖存下來的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.12,0:09:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.62,0:09:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟會在這裡遇到你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遒是命運嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.93,0:09:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.47,0:09:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.64,0:09:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說你們的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.31,0:09:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不問也知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.27,0:09:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命定為主君的在這世上只有一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.11,0:09:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索特大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.38,0:09:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就委派給我古倫貝路多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.86,0:09:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.42,0:09:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽過你的傳聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.33,0:09:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖是一介凡人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.00,0:09:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻是從他的蝕中生還的豪傑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.88,0:09:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.40,0:10:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人多勢罘攻打一個在如此偏僻的森林隱居的老太婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.35,0:10:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實在有損武人的名譽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.18,0:10:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻是向鷹示忠的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.36,0:10:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是本人才要求與他們同行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.86,0:10:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到會遇到你這樣的武者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.74,0:10:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,著沉重的步伐來到此地也值了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.96,0:10:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古力菲斯的命令 為何他要把婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.58,0:10:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我古倫貝路多 特作為鷹之團的一介武夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.36,0:10:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和黑色劍士單挑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.97,0:10:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.14,0:10:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.26,0:10:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才他說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.85,0:10:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼鷹之團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.02,0:10:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.76,0:10:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊斯多洛先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.66,0:11:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呀 魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.20,0:11:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廑法怎麼了 魔法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.78,0:11:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的心很亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.29,0:11:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使不出魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.08,0:11:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.13,0:11:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個快從這裡出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.80,0:11:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞爾彼高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.05,0:11:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能用你的羽毛羽毛撢子做點什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.08,0:11:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 只會把火勢增大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.84,0:11:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人 你在哪 回答我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.47,0:11:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希凱兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.85,0:11:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.92,0:11:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好聽著 我的嫡傳弟子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.08,0:11:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那個交給黑色劍士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是 莫非是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.24,0:11:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.82,0:11:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.41,0:11:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快些 可怕的敵人迫近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.70,0:11:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去劍士先生會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.42,0:11:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這樣的話師傅你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.56,0:11:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.17,0:12:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一刻已來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.59,0:12:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.44,0:12:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這樣 這樣太殘忍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.14,0:12:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該更寧靜地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.64,0:12:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是被這樣的火包圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.00,0:12:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本就背負的這樣的罪業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.69,0:12:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類違背時間的法則延命至今是多麼罪孽深重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.50,0:12:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為魔法師的你應該清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.58,0:12:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.94,0:12:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 果然還是太寂寞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.58,0:12:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 不管是陽光下的膝枕 還是和格雷姆們的午茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.13,0:12:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有 所有都會消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.01,0:12:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都要被燒毀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.10,0:12:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希凱兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.44,0:13:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼凶狠的一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.03,0:13:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明還是人類的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.16,0:13:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量卻高於一般的使徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.08,0:13:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們有什麼資格 自稱鷹之團啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.20,0:13:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙 剛才亂來那麼一下裂了好幾根骨頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.28,0:13:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起的劍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.88,0:13:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了我兩戰錘竟然沒有斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.04,0:13:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你這算什麼戰鬥方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.24,0:13:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連抵抗都不行 只是一直被打飛不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.99,0:13:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站著說話不腰疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連甲冑都沒有赤膊上陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.46,0:14:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龍老大也是真喜歡這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.60,0:14:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也趕緊做完工作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.88,0:14:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把魔女的腦袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.68,0:14:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.68,0:14:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你他媽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.27,0:14:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.68,0:14:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來做這傢伙的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.40,0:14:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也忍不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.23,0:14:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙把同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.90,0:14:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是命令 你們把魔女的腦袋帶過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.74,0:14:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正打得火熱的時候 你要去追女人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.46,0:14:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點也不像你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.79,0:14:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對你來說 戰鬥才是一切 不死者啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.54,0:14:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要會錯意 能阻止你的只有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.60,0:14:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.89,0:15:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都和平時不一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.35,0:15:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 喔 都是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.22,0:15:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女的弟子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.07,0:15:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事 剛退冶了獸鬼 這次是怪人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.10,0:15:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是 使徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.08,0:15:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們不想死就告訴我魔女在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.41,0:15:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過就是說了也會被燒死罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.22,0:15:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.10,0:15:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不趕緊跑出去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.02,0:15:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很殘酷 但是要去救科羅拉的話我們也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.02,0:15:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去寶物庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.06,0:15:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡有必須交給凱茲的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.86,0:15:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.69,0:15:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這就是師傅的願望的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.16,0:15:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人是不是我的命運 我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.75,0:16:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在能救他的只有我這個魔法師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.42,0:16:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有身為靈樹森林的魔女科羅拉的弟子的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.22,0:16:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能做到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.97,0:16:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.54,0:16:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要給的東西 是那個護符嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.20,0:16:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 但不止這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.77,0:16:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅上了護符的咒物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.92,0:16:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險且強力的某種咒物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.53,0:16:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.53,0:16:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是那個色劍士嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.66,0:16:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說打敗了不少使徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.84,0:16:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那個不死的索特打的不分上下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.36,0:16:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的宿敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.14,0:16:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是這種窩囊廢嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.47,0:16:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索特大人運氣真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能遇上那種勁敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.35,0:17:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對武者來說 戰場即是聖地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.73,0:17:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,置於死地而後生才是本分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.36,0:17:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你好像不配武者的榮耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.53,0:17:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個怪物現在裝什麼武者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我陶醉的混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.91,0:17:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為戰士 你不配死在我戰錘之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.59,0:17:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化為碎片消散吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.26,0:17:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.85,0:17:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 大隻的玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.86,0:17:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是希凱兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.48,0:17:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要進到哪裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.95,0:18:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.50,0:18:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.81,0:18:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真是要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.10,0:18:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像希凱兒說的 傷囗裂開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.15,0:18:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我處理不了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.36,0:18:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 這樣就算穿上那個也動不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.99,0:18:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拖拖拉拉的 火就要燒過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.57,0:18:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確現在這個狀態穿上那個還能保命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.32,0:18:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.91,0:18:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女 魔女在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.04,0:18:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 是那些傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.75,0:18:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.80,0:18:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.21,0:18:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡果然還是要靠的我的魔法撐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.68,0:19:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是把大家捲入危險的我的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.56,0:19:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 痛痛痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.15,0:19:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要這麼做嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.31,0:19:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給傷成這樣的凱茲穿上甲冑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.90,0:19:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只能相信希凱兒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.32,0:19:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 我不管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.08,0:19:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了 怪獸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.92,0:19:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耍小聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.00,0:19:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲在那裡了黑色劍士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.92,0:19:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今還要醜態百出嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.23,0:19:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我 好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.23,0:19:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明吃下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.76,0:19:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明應該咬死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.17,0:20:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.27,0:20:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.07,0:20:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不光是厲害了 怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.03,0:20:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才還都站不起來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.20,0:20:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這就不厚道了 這麼厲害的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.16,0:20:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在退治獸鬼的時候就該給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.91,0:20:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個不是那麼簡單的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.96,0:20:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個傢伙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.00,0:21:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從動作上看完全變了個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.46,0:21:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 那把劍確實是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.68,0:21:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.06,0:21:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很懷念啊 老友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.50,0:21:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要讓他踏上同樣的道路嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.73,0:21:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一樣化為冥府魔道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.73,0:21:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這甲胃是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.65,0:21:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上的時候 傷囗就像假的一樣不痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.78,0:21:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這都無所謂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.04,0:21:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼痛都 無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.46,0:21:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.88,0:21:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這股在體內沸騰的衝動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.16,0:21:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體中有什麼 狂暴的東西湧現出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.43,0:21:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 身 體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.60,0:21:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.25,0:21:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 血 肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.89,0:21:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.64,0:21:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 一 切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.48,0:22:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.11,0:22:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 骨 髓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.90,0:22:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獻上你的一切吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.82,0:22:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 生 命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.62,0:22:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲冑的形狀
